tafsir[25]{c,v,t}:
  84,1,"Si kammu on fettii sabi tellaade Malayka en e mammba."
  84,2,"Mbo heɗii joomi makko wondude ɗoftaare, woodani mbo hakke e ɗuum."
  84,3,"Si Alla fooɗti leydi ndi hono no nguru fooɗtirte nih."
  84,4,"Ndi werlii ko woni e mum e ngaluuji e maayɓe, ndi acciti gaa mum en."
  84,5,"Mbo heɗii joomi makko wondude ɗoftaare, woodani mbo e hakke kadi woodanii Mbo e ɗuum."
  84,6,"Eehey ma aade, ko a golloowo jam wolla bone, ko a pottoowo e joom ma ñande darnga ngam O yoɓ ma golle ma."
  84,7,"Tawi ko oon tottiraaɗo ɗerawol golle mum junnga ñaama."
  84,8,"Yaama o haasbe haasbeere newiinde o holle golle mum ko aldah e nanngiteede."
  84,9,"O ruttoo e koreeji makko ko p beltiiɗo."
  84,10,"Tawi ko oon tottiraaɗo deftere mum nana makko ummorde caggal keeci makko."
  84,11,"Ma o noddu halkaare e dow hoore makko."
  84,12,"O naata yiite jahannama o suma e nguleeki mum."
  84,13,"Pellet o woniina beltiiɗo e nder koreeji makko sabu ko o wonnoo ko e heefeeru e goopi."
  84,14,"Pellet o sikkiina o ruttataaka e nguurndam caggal maayde."
  84,15,"Oho kay, ma Alla ruttu mbo e nguurndam hono no tagirnoo mbo adanum nih, Alla noon na sutii alhaali makko hay ndiga wirnataako Mbo, ma O yoɓ mbo golle makko."
  84,16,"Alla woondirii mboɗeeri koode saanga mutal naange e jookli."
  84,17,"O woondiri jemma e kombo soomi."
  84,18,"O woondirii lewru si ndu timmii."
  84,19,"Ma on pawandire e mbaadi tagu e alhaali caggal alhaali ummaade e toɓɓere refti heɗɗere refti husre refti heen nguurndam caggal maayde."
  84,20,"Hol ko haɗi heefereeɓe goonɗinde Alla, e ñalngu cakkatiiɗo."
  84,21,"Si Quraana janngaama e mum en ɓe cujjatah."
  84,22,"Woni ko ɓeen heefereeɓe ɓe pennat ko nelaaɓe mum ngaddani ɓe."
  84,23,"Ko Alla anndi ko wirnii e ɓerɗe mum en, hay huunde wirnataako Mbo e golle mum en."
  84,24,"Habruɓe-aan nelaaɗo- ko fadiɓe e leɓte muusɗe."
  84,25,"Si wonah ɓeen gomɗimɓe Allah e Nulaaɗo Makko on, ɓe golli moƴƴuɗi yamiraaɗi ɗin, hino woodani ɓe njoɓdi duumotoondi ndi taƴatah, woni Aljanna."
